Alarm system for Domoticz

There was no real alarm system for Domoticz. Some scripts and blokeys are available, but they do not meet my expectations. So I created this plugin.

The plugin is tested to works on a Raspberry Pi 3b.

To install the plugin login to the Raspberry Pi.
  
      cd /home/<username>/domoticz/plugin
  
      git clone https://github.com/Wizzard72/Domoticz-Alarm
      
      sudo systemctl restart domoticz.service

